content.description:
I'm now on the OpenStreetMap directions page. To find driving directions from Central Park to Times Square, I need to:
1. Enter 'Central Park, New York' in the 'From' textbox
2. Enter 'Times Square, New York' in the 'To' textbox
3. Ensure 'Car (OSRM)' is selected in the dropdown (which appears to be already selected)
4. Click the 'Go' button to get the directions

I'll start by filling in the 'From' field which has bid '158'.
